Class DeclReader.DeclPpt

  • Object
    • DeclReader.DeclPpt
  • Enclosing class:
    DeclReader

    public static class DeclReader.DeclPpt
extends Object
    Information about the program point that is contained in the decl file. This consists of the ppt name and a list of the declared variables.
